==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Snowshoe
<hw>Snow"shoe`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A slight frame of
wood three or four feet long and about one third as wide, with thongs or
cords stretched across it, and having a support and holder for the foot;
-- used by persons for walking on soft snow.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Snowshoeing</ent>⟦br⟧
